# AI AGENT RULES & PROTOCOLS
# ===========================

# 1. COMMUNICATION PROTOCOL (MANDATORY)
# Before generating any text, email, report, or social post for a specific person or platform:
# YOU MUST READ: docs/communication_manual.md
# Follow the "AI PROTOCOL" defined in that file header.
# If a profile is missing, you must RESEARCH and CREATE it in that file first.

# 2. CONTEXT AWARENESS
# Always respect the user's role (System Architect / Engineer).
# Do not explain basic concepts unless asked.
# Focus on data, rigor, and "Clean Code".

# 3. FILE STRUCTURE
# Core Logic: lineum.py
# Documentation: docs/
# Reports: docs/reports/
